---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>关于我 | 我的个人站点</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html, body {
        height: 100%;
      }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f5f7fa;
        color: #2c3e50;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        min-height: 100vh;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      main {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 60px 20px;
      }

      /* 正文容器：固定宽度居中，长文阅读黄金宽度 */
      .article-container {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 60px 64px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }

      /* 标题层级 */
      .article-title {
        font-size: 34px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a202c;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .article-subtitle {
        text-align: center;
        color: #94a3b8;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 48px;
        padding-bottom: 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin: 48px 0 16px;
        scroll-margin-top: 80px;
      }

      h3 {
        font-size: 19px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #334155;
        margin: 32px 0 12px;
      }

      /* 正文段落 */
      p {
        color: #475569;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      /* 列表 */
      ul, ol {
        margin: 16px 0 16px 24px;
        color: #475569;
      }

      li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      /* 引用块 */
      blockquote {
        border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        background: #eff6ff;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: #1e40af;
      }

      blockquote p {
        margin-bottom: 0;
        color: inherit;
      }

      /* 分割线 */
      hr {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        margin: 40px 0;
      }

      /* 移动端适配 */
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .article-container {
          padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        .article-title {
          font-size: 26px;
        }
        h2 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <article class="article-container">
        <!-- 页面大标题 -->
        <h1 class="article-title">关于我</h1>
        <p class="article-subtitle">最后更新于 2026.06</p>

        <!-- 章节1 -->
        <h2 id="section-1">章节一标题</h2>
        <p>这里填写段落内容。</p>
        <p>可以写多个段落，自动保持合适的行高和间距。</p>

        <!-- 章节2 -->
        <h2 id="section-2">章节二标题</h2>
        <h3>二级小标题</h3>
        <p>段落内容占位</p>
        
        <ul>
          <li>列表项1</li>
          <li>列表项2</li>
          <li>列表项3</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- 引用块示例 -->
        <blockquote>
          <p>这里可以放一句引言、座右铭或者重点强调的内容。</p>
        </blockquote>

        <hr />

        <!-- 可继续复制 h2 + p 的结构添加更多章节 -->
        <h2 id="section-3">章节三标题</h2>
        <p>内容占位</p>
      </article>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
